Installation
============

Please see INSTALL for more detailed installation instructions.

Coding Style
============

If you want to contribute code or you are already a developer
then please respect our coding style. We only enforce a style
to make a better maintenance. If you do not like the style or
you have an idea to improve the style then please start a
discussion on our developer list.

perltidy --profile=perltidyrc -b `find . -name "*.pm" | grep -v "/\.svn"`
